#: ../case.rst:20
msgid "Here are some requirements that we want to meet when the site is done:"
msgstr ""

#: ../case.rst:22
msgid "As a visitor I want to find current information on the conference"
msgstr ""
"Como un visitante, yo quiero encontrar información actualizada en la "
"conferencia."

#: ../case.rst:23
msgid "As a visitor I want to register for the conference"
msgstr "Como visitante, yo quiero registrarme para la conferencia."

#: ../case.rst:24
msgid "As a visitor I want to see the talks and sort them by my preferences"
msgstr ""
"Como visitante, yo quiero ver las charlas y ordenarlas por mis "
"preferencias."

#: ../case.rst:25
#, fuzzy
msgid "As a speaker I want to be able to submit talks"
msgstr "Como un ponente, yo quiero ser capaz de agregar charlas."

#: ../case.rst:26
msgid "As a speaker I want to see and edit my submitted talks"
msgstr "Como un ponente, yo quiero ver y editar mis charlas enviadas."

#: ../case.rst:27
msgid "As an organizer I want to see a list of all proposed talks"
msgstr "Como organizador, yo quiero ver una lista de todas las charlas propuestas."

#: ../case.rst:28
msgid ""
"As an organizer I want to have an overview about how many people "
"registered"
msgstr ""
"Como organizador, yo quiero tener un resumen acerca de cuantas personas "
"están registradas."

#: ../case.rst:29
#, fuzzy
msgid "As a jury member I want to vote on talks"
msgstr "Como miembro de jurado, yo quiero votar en las charlas."

#: ../case.rst:30
#, fuzzy
msgid "As a jury member I want to decide which talks to accept, and which not"
msgstr ""
"Como miembro del jurado, yo quiero decidir, cuales charlas aceptar, y "
"cuales no."

